examples.en: Colds do not respond to antibiotics.
The whole family had caught colds.
Smokers had the highest incidence of colds.
The colds of January did not hinder him from sending messengers.
So many children are away this week with colds.
Vitamin C is popularly believed to prevent colds.
She has a theory that drinking milk prevents colds.
Do dress warmly, there are a lot of colds about just now.
